beer.beer_description:
Like the blooming of magnolias and blossoms, the release of Saison heralds the coming of Spring! Our Spring Saison is a modern twist on a traditional farmhouse style, that harks back to the days when farm workers were paid in beer. 

Funky, fruity and fresh with French Saison yeast and Australian hops - Ella and Cascade. Spring Saison is crisp and dry with wine-like, spice and mandarin characters.

Spring Saison is part of the Two Birds ongoing Seasonal range and is available until end of November.
